        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Mobile</placeName>
                <date>October 21 5612</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>!</p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">Dear sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(12)">The <persName>Rev. A. Ansel</persName><lb/>
                <sic>formely</sic> from <placeName>Liverpool</placeName>, died here on <date>Sept
                    8</date> last. I am informed<lb/> he has a brother &amp; other relations in
                    <placeName>England</placeName> living, for their information<lb/> I would
                    <sic>respectfuly</sic> request you (in as much the Occident circulates<lb/> in
                    <placeName>England</placeName>) to insert a Notice of his death in the next
                    <sic>numbre</sic><lb/> of your valuable <sic>periodicle</sic>. He has been
                officiating as/<hi rend="sup">in</hi>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
                <add>“busosal” JE transliteration</add><lb/> in <placeName>Claiborne Ala</placeName>
                for about 8 months; he came here to<lb/> circumcise a child, was taken ill &amp;
                after 8 days lingering he<lb/> died here &amp; was buried with all due honor in our
                    <sic>burring</sic> ground.<lb/> His Mohel instrument (all the property he left)
                is in my<lb/> possession &amp; are to be retained by order of the president<lb/> as
                a memento for his child, which is now living at <placeName>Buffalo<lb/> N.
                    Y.</placeName> as <persName>Mr. Ansel</persName> informed me previous to his
                death.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I regret very much for not being able to remit you any<lb/> money. I
                have not <sic>collecting</sic> a dollar since the last I <sic>remitit</sic><lb/>
                you, the scarcity of money is very great. the rivers are very low<lb/> &amp; not
                navigable &amp; country <sic>peapol</sic> cannot come to our city<lb/> Business of
                every dis<add>?</add> are all nearly sus<add>?</add>, but as<lb/> soon <add>?</add>
                I will remit at once. <sic>Respectfuly</sic></p>
            <p rend="align(center)">Yours Truly</p>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <hi rend="underline">
                    <persName role="author">B M Emanuel</persName>
                </hi>
            </p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>, Editor of the</p>
            <p rend="align(center)">Occident &amp; american jewish <sic>advocat</sic></p>
            <p rend="align(center)indent(3)">|<placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia
                    Pa</hi></placeName></p>
